sections.heading: park system; violations; penalty
sections.text: Any person violating sections 37-337 to 37-348 or the rules and regulations governing the public use or administration of a state park shall be guilty of a Class III misdemeanor.SourceLaws 1959, c. 436, ยง 13, p. 1468;Laws 1977, LB 39, ยง 295;R.S.1943, (1996), ยง 81-815
